===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-get a grip.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Verb===
'''[[get]] [[a]] [[grip]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[relax]]; to [[calm]] [[down]]; to stop being [[angry]]; to come to one's senses or become more [[rational]].
#:''He needs to '''get a grip''' if he's getting that angry over such a little thing.''

===Usage note===
*Usually used in the [[imperative]].